{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/delete-properties-from-a-javascript-object","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Obrisite Svojstva iz JavaScript Objekta","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Svojstva iz objekata mozemo i obrisati ovako:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">delete ourDog.bark;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Primer:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const ourDog = {\n  \"name\": \"Camper\",\n  \"legs\": 4,\n  \"tails\": 1,\n  \"friends\": [\"everything!\"],\n  \"bark\": \"bow-wow\"\n};\n\ndelete ourDog.bark;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Nakon poslednje prikazane linije iznad, <code>ourDog</code> izgleda ovako:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">{\n  \"name\": \"Camper\",\n  \"legs\": 4,\n  \"tails\": 1,\n  \"friends\": [\"everything!\"]\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56bbb991ad1ed5201cd392d3","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Obrisite svojstvo <code>tails</code> iz <code>myDog</code>. Mozete koristiti notaciju tacke ili uglastih zagrada.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":17560,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/delete-properties-from-a-javascript-object"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nconst myDog = {\n  \"name\": \"Happy Coder\",\n  \"legs\": 4,\n  \"tails\": 1,\n  \"friends\": [\"freeCodeCamp Campers\"],\n  \"bark\": \"woof\"\n};\n\n// Only change code below this line\n","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da obri